high_descs: Move forward, then turn left, to go toward the oven.
Take the potato from the microwave, above the oven.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge.
Turn around, go straight, then turn left to return to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward to the fridge then turn left and walk to the stove that's on your left and then turn left to face it.
Get the potato out of the microwave above the stove and then close the door.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge that's on your right and stand facing it.
Put it in the fridge and cool it down and then get it back out and close the door.
Put the potato back in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the front of the stove.
Open the microwave, remove the potato in the microwave and close the door.
Walk the potato to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge, close the doors, then open and remove.
Take the potato back to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato back in, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Prepare a potato in the microwave.
